          "growthOriented": false,
          "selfCompassion": true,
          "evidenceBased": "Brown (2010) - 归属感与爱"
        },
        {
          "id": "rabbit_msg_006",
          "text": "今天心情怎么样？我愿意听 🌸 不用组织语言，我就在这里。",
          "ppFramework": "relationships",
          "growthOriented": false,
          "selfCompassion": false,
          "evidenceBased": "Rogers (1951) - 无条件积极关注"
        },
        {
          "id": "rabbit_msg_007",
          "text": "给自己一个拥抱吧 🤗 你刚才展现的坚韧，是你的性格优势之一。",
