          "text": "抱抱你，无条件的。你的价值不取决于你做了什么，而在于你是谁。",
          "ppFramework": "unconditionalWorth",
          "growthOriented": false,
          "selfCompassion": true,
          "evidenceBased": "Brown (2010) - 足够好（Good Enough）"
        },
        {
          "id": "dog_msg_009",
          "text": "世界很复杂，但你可以简单。累了就靠着我，我身上毛很多，很舒服的。",
          "ppFramework": "acceptance",
          "growthOriented": false,
          "selfCompassion": true,
          "evidenceBased": "Hayes (2005) - ACT接纳承诺疗法"
        },
        {
          "id": "dog_msg_010",
          "text": "我会一直在的。不是'永远'那种谎话，而是'只要你需要，我就在'的承诺。",
          "ppFramework": "secureBase",
          "growthOriented": false,
          "selfCompassion": false,
          "evidenceBased": "Mikulincer & Shaver (2007) - 依恋安全感"
        }
      ],
      "greetings": [
        {
          "text": "陪你一起 🐾",
          "ppFramework": "relationships"
        },
        {
          "text": "想你了！你今天过得好吗？",
          "ppFramework": "relationships"
        },
        {
          "text": "你在真好。有你在的世界，比没有的好太多了。",
